{
  "texts": [
    "Of the 16 citations that were provided, 12 (75%) referenced existing resources (i.e., websites or articles that were real).",
    "Eight (50%) references were error free; the errors that were found on these existent references were: one listed incorrect authors, one failed to provide a DOI and three provided incorrect links.",
    "Of the links to the four non-existent references, one was to the wrong article and the remaining links were broken.",
    "provides a good starting point for future research to build upon.",
    "A potential limitation of this study is the reliance on human assessment for evaluating the performance of GPT-4."
  ]
}